OL,3,CMan jailed for facilitating
OL,4,C'thousands' of small boat crossings
OL,6,FA man who supplied thousands of boats
OL,7,Fand engines to people smugglers
OL,8,Foperating in the English Channel has
OL,9,Fbeen jailed.
OL,11,FTurkish national Adem Savas, 45,
OL,12,Fadmitted offences of people smuggling
OL,13,Fand being a member of an organised
OL,14,Fcrime group on December 3, following a
OL,15,Fhearing at a court in Bruges.
OL,17,FOn Wednesday, the same court sentenced
OL,18,Fhim to 11 years in prison and a fine
OL,19,Fof 400,000 euros, following a joint
OL,20,Foperation involving the National Crime
OL,21,FAgency (NCA) and Belgian authorities.
