OL,6,FThree co-defendants were given
OL,7,Fsentences totalling 38 years.
OL,9,FSavas had been detained at Schiphol
OL,10,FAirport in Amsterdam on November 13
OL,11,F2024, before being extradited to
OL,12,FBelgium to face charges.
OL,14,FHe was initially identified by the NCA
OL,15,Ffollowing an investigation into
OL,16,FKurdish crime boss Hewa Rahimpur.
