OL,3,CMan jailed for facilitating
OL,4,C'thousands' of small boat crossings
OL,6,FRahimpur ran a major Europe-wide
OL,7,Fsmuggling ring believed to be behind
OL,8,Fthe movement of more than 10,000
OL,9,Fmigrants in small boat crossings to
OL,10,Fthe UK.
OL,12,FHe was arrested in 2022 by the NCA
OL,13,Fnear Ilford, east London, where he was
OL,14,Fliving at the time, and extradited to
OL,15,FBelgium.
