OL,4,C'thousands' of small boat crossings
OL,6,FRahimpur was convicted and jailed for
OL,7,F11 years in October 2023. This was
OL,8,Flater increased to 13 years on appeal.
OL,9,FOther members of his network were also
OL,10,Fsubsequently convicted in France and
OL,11,Fthe UK.
OL,13,FAnalysis of phones and devices seized
OL,14,Ffollowing Rahimpur's arrest revealed
OL,15,Fthat his key supplier of boats and
OL,16,Fengines was Savas, and the two were in
OL,17,Fregular contact.
