OL,3,CMan jailed for facilitating
OL,4,C'thousands' of small boat crossings
OL,6,FAt the time, Savas was the main
OL,7,Fimporter of cheap 'Parsun' branded
OL,8,Foutboard engines sourced from China,
OL,9,Fthe type most frequently used by gangs
OL,10,Foperating small boats in the Channel.
OL,12,FThe NCA, working with Belgian
OL,13,Fcounterparts, investigated how boats
OL,14,Fand engines sourced by Savas were
OL,15,Fmoved overland from Turkey into
OL,16,FBulgaria, and then across Europe to
OL,17,FGermany, where they would be stored
OL,18,Fbefore being used in the Channel.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/10
