OL,4,C'thousands' of small boat crossings
OL,6,FCharging on average around #4,000 for
OL,7,Fpackages of boats and engines, Savas
OL,8,Fis likely to have made millions over
OL,9,Fthe time of his offending.
OL,11,FThe NCA's Director General of
OL,12,FOperations, Rob Jones, said Savas was
OL,13,F"without doubt the most significant
OL,14,Fsupplier of boats and engines to
OL,15,Fpeople smuggling gangs involved in
OL,16,Forganising deadly crossings in the
OL,17,FChannel".
