OL,6,F"He pretended to run a legitimate
OL,7,Fmaritime supply company, but in
OL,8,Freality, he knew exactly how the
OL,9,Fequipment he provided would be used,"
OL,10,Fhe said.
OL,12,F"Boats and engines supplied by Savas
OL,13,Fwere likely involved in numerous fatal
OL,14,Fevents in the Channel ` he made money
OL,15,Ffrom each of those."
