OL,6,FOne exchange of messages between Savas
OL,7,Fand Rahimpur in November 2021 followed
OL,8,Fthe deaths of 27 migrants, when their
OL,9,Fboat sank in the Channel.
OL,11,FRahimpur sent Savas five separate
OL,12,Fimages of a white rubber boat, along
OL,13,Fwith a screen grab from a news website
OL,14,Fshowing how an identical boat had been
OL,15,Fused in the fatal crossing.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G8/10
