OL,6,FAnother video sent showed boxes of
OL,7,Fboats, controlled by Savas'
OL,8,Fassociates, piled high in a warehouse,
OL,9,Fwhile investigators also recovered a
OL,10,Fprice list for boats, engines and life
OL,11,Fjackets.
OL,13,FAn operation to track his movements
OL,14,Fwas instigated, involving the NCA,
OL,15,FBelgian and Dutch law enforcement, and
OL,16,FBelgian prosecutors.
